      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:5:2:107:4",
      "text": [
        " كَرِهَ أَبُو عَبْدِ اللَّهِ ( عليه السلام ) بَيْعَ الْعَصِيرِ بِتَأْخِيرٍ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Abu Ali Al Ashary, from Muhammad Bin Abdul Jabbar, from Safwan, from Ibn Muskan, from Yazeed Bin Khaleefa who said, ",
          "‘Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> disliked selling the juice with a delay (on credit, lest it turns into wine)’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "4. Abu Ali al-Ash’ariy has narrated from Muhammad ibn ‘Abd al-Jabbar from Safwan from ibn Muskan from Yazid ibn Khalifah who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, disliked selling juice for deferred payment.” "
        ]
      }
